This are the fields filled:

stem.NAME       name of the font
stem.YSIZE      ta_YSize
stem.FLAGS      ta_Flags
stem.STYLE      ta_Style


This function returns the error code 10 if  the  font  number  is  out  of
range.
@ENDNODE

